Title: Drupal.NET
Description: A port of the STUNNING, well known CMS/CMFx "Drupal" to the .NET Framework. Combining The greatest open source CMS with the greatest development platform. It will have the same architecture and will support Drupal modules and themes out of the box.
HomeWiki:
BREAKING NEWS


The Official port the STUNNING, well known CMS/CMFx "Drupal" to the .NET Framework project is currently under development.
Combining The greatest open source CMS with the greatest development platform.

It will have the same architecture and will support Drupal modules and themes out of the box.

You can also review the project page on sourceforge at: https://sourceforge.net/projects/drupal-net/
Drupal Group at: http://groups.drupal.org/drupalnet
